   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Chairemon, secretary of the elders of the 7th year, to Horos, elder in the same year, greeting. I have received to the account of various items(?) of the same year two hundred drachmai, equals 200 drachmai, on account of salary, and expenses in addition. The 9th year, Phamenoth 7.</ab>
